William R. Fatt

Age : 66Public asset : 1,544,379 USDLinked companies :  Bank of Nova Scotia -  Canadian Pacific Railway Limited 





Summary 



Mr. William R. Fatt is Chief Executive Officer at Fairmont Hotels & Resorts, Inc., Chief Executive Officer at Fairmont Hotels, Inc. and Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Fairmont Raffles Hotels International, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at Canadian Pacific Railway Ltd., Canadian Pacific Railway Co., Bank of Nova Scotia and The Jim Pattison Group, Inc. Mr. Fatt was previously employed as Chairman by The Cadillac Fairview Corp. Ltd., a Trustee by Legacy Hotels Real Estate Investment Trust, Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Canadian Pacific Hotels & Resorts, Inc., Chief Financial Officer by Canadian Pacific Ltd., and Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by FRHI Hotels & Resorts SARL.He also served on the board at Enbridge Gas Distribution, Inc., Enbridge, Inc., Encana Corp. and Sun Life Financial, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from York University.



