William R. Fatt's Biography




			Mr. Fatt is a corporate director. He is the former Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of FRHI Hotels & Resorts. He is currently a member of the board of directors of The Jim Pattison Group Inc. and the Bank of Nova Scotia. Previously, Mr. Fatt was Chairman of the Board of Cadillac Fairview Corporation and a director of Encana Corporation, Sun Life Financial Inc. and Enbridge Inc.

 

Mr. Fatt holds a B.A. (Economics) from York University.

 

Mr. Fatt brings to the Board over 30 years of finance, investment, capital markets and international experience.
		
Source: Canadian Pacific Railway Limited on 03/02/2017
		
	

 






