Fatt, William R. - The Wall Street Transcript











































 





































William R. Fatt
WILLIAM R. FATT became Chief Executive Officer for Fairmont Hotels &
Resorts Inc. (formerly Canadian Pacific Hotels) on January 1, 1998. Mr.
Fatt is also Vice Chairman of Legacy Hotels Real Estate Investment
Trust. Prior to his role at Fairmont Hotels & Resorts, Mr. Fatt held
various positions with Canadian Pacific Ltd. from 1988, most recently as
Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer. Mr. Fatt is a
member of the Board of Directors of Fairmont Hotels & Resorts Inc.,
Legacy Hotels Real Estate Investment Trust, Enbridge Inc., EnCana
Corporation (formerly PanCanadian Energy Corporation), Sun Life
Financial Inc. and The Jim Pattison Group.
